{"tid":529703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長者重返職場有無計？耆康會推「實習耆兵」月薪$12,000","createTime":"2018-01-15T04:44:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-15T05:26:55.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a44aa58104edf6358c6e7ffbf0e1675008e83ac1","tid":529703,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T04:44:02.000Z","msg":"本港人口老化嚴重，有資深家庭醫生指完全退休後長者行動不便機會有約66%，健康轉差及患病等機會亦增加。相反長者繼續工作有助減低患認知障礙症風險，有研究指65歲比60歲長者退休患上認知障礙症風險减少約15%。<br />\n<br />\n資深家庭醫生莫昆洋說，長者退休後時間難打發，會影響身心健康，有適合工作有助保持適量運動、幫助思考靈活及心理健康。因工作擴濶人際關係、保持社交、自信心、社會地方。<br />\n<br />\n雀巢三花品牌與耆康會合作，招聘3位實習耆兵，擔任大使協辦活動、接聽電話、健康團隊走訪日間長者中心。每周工作4天，每天工作6小時，月薪12,000元。<br />\n<br />\n耆康會行政總監梁綺眉指，香港55歲及以上人士只有約20%屬勞動人口，長者就業人數仍明顯低於鄰近南韓31%、新加坡26%、日本22%。建議想重返職場長者避免擺出高姿態、抱開放態度、自我增值、與時代接軌，以活到老、學到老態度重新出發。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180115/57709164\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180115%2F57709164&d=e%2FtsVztfPOQ9Mcxu9sHNkjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=17d618e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180115%2F57709164&h=21714133\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180115/57709164</a>"},{"pid":"17fc0fc9640ec56791caedd1ceb558f45611b27c","tid":529703,"uid":20072,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T04:45:23.000Z","msg":"做到100歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"035fd66208a9619ff0c09804a1fb288328ee6bef","tid":529703,"uid":101396,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T04:55:30.000Z","msg":"份工仲正過我個份"},{"pid":"8bb15d9fcdc6c60e05933262bcddce7b06772e3b","tid":529703,"uid":5253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T04:56:47.000Z","msg":"廢青有冇得做"},{"pid":"60fc3d992da5e29f13c23f0c22faff38e686fa22","tid":529703,"uid":64131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T04:57:51.000Z","msg":"啲所謂長者求鳩期有份野做下<br />\n發揮下交際手腕就好滿足<br />\n志在有個角色比佢"},{"pid":"c1d44c0044f043ac14a59a7da8d881ecf45894ae","tid":529703,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T04:58:52.000Z","msg":"廢青唔加人工，拎去補貼請廢老 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efab936c30a14910c238799d2fdb371a170b9584","tid":529703,"uid":44725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T05:00:42.000Z","msg":"每周工作4天,每天6小時<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee7f7fd2a3a90c82d218f22413e15669a3cc2054","tid":529703,"uid":438,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T05:02:09.000Z","msg":"仲高人工過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e77303588101e71622f7c839568a488e46b65579","tid":529703,"uid":60291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T05:02:10.000Z","msg":"時薪過100<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf297e06daa1e32bcef2513b2ba8283b955ae0fb","tid":529703,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T05:02:33.000Z","msg":"有萬二請中年人唔好"},{"pid":"d510defc2124d53be37059e014566836546caf8a","tid":529703,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T05:03:04.000Z","msg":"時薪111蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa9f7339